The KiCad source code is separated into multiple repositories.
git-kicad.sh will fetch and package them for you.

They are combined as follows:
bzr export <packaging folder>/ lp:kicad/4.0
git clone https://github.com/KiCad/kicad-i18n <packaging folder>/kicad-i18n
git clone https://github.com/KiCad/kicad-doc <packaging folder>/kicad-doc
git clone https://github.com/KiCad/kicad-library <packaging folder>/kicad-library
git clone https://github.com/KiCad/*.pretty <packaging folder>/kicad-pretty/$pretty
